Speaker 2: Hi! It's been a busy week, but pretty good overall. How about you? How's Warwick treating you?

Speaker 1: Couldn't have said it better myself. It's all about making a difference, one day at a time. 
Speaker 2: Absolutely! Well, it was nice catching up. Let's do this again soon. 
Speaker 1: Definitely, I'll look forward to it. Have a great day!
Speaker 2: You too, take care!
